spec_data.Name: python3-alchimia
spec_data.Description:
alchimia lets you use most of the SQLAlchemy-core API with Twisted,
it does not allow you to use the ORM.
This package provides Python 3 build of alchimia.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 19 Sep 2017 08:51:06 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A Python library that integrates Twisted with SqlAlchemy
